  "description": "A sweeping aerial view of a city sprawling towards a large body of water. The city is densely packed with buildings, mostly low-rise, creating a patchwork of rooftops. In the distance, a skyline is visible along the water's edge, with structures including what appear to be bridges and possibly skyscrapers. The water body is wide and calm, reflecting the overcast sky. A green foreground suggests a hillside or elevated vantage point. The overall scene is bathed in soft, diffused light due to the cloudy sky.",
